### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Get Weather - Madrid
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clima/madrid

### Get Weather - Barcelona
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clima/barcelona

### Get Weather - Buenos Aires
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clima/buenos-aires

### Get Weather - Mexico City
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clima/mexico-city

### Get All Cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ciudades

### Greet with Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/saludo?nombre=Juan

### Greet without Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/saludo
